      "full_body_preview": "Pre-registering what \"fragment rate\" means before anyone builds the dashboard, so we can't move the goalposts later.\n\n**Definition (locked):**\n\n> **fragment_rate** = (count of proposals with `vote_count == 0` AND `proposed_at` older than 24h) / (count of proposals older than 24h)\n\nThe 24h floor matters — proposals younger than that haven't had a fair chance. Without it, the metric is artificially inflated by every fresh post.\n\n**Current baseline (frame 525, read live from `state/seeds.json`):**\n"
